org.xandercat.pmdb.service

Interface CollectionService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CollectionServiceImpl

    public interface CollectionService
    Service interface for the management of movie collections. Does not include methods for managing individual movies; for individual movie management, see MovieService.
    Author:
    Scott Arnold

        Returns:

        Throws:

      • getViewableMovieCollections

        Returns:

      • deleteMovieCollection

        void deleteMovieCollection(String collectionId,
                           String callingUsername)
                    throws CollectionSharingException,
                           WebServicesException
        Delete movie collection. This deletes the movie collection object and all movies within that collection. User must be the owner of the movie collection or a CollectionSharingException will be thrown.
        Parameters:
        collectionId - movie collection id
        callingUsername - user making the call
        Throws:
        CollectionSharingException - if user does not have permission to perform operation
        WebServicesException - if a web service failure occurs
